          "reviewTitle": "I love this product",
          "reviewText": "This foundation is great. It doesn't take much to cover. I get a lot of compliments on my skin, and I'm 73, because it cover a multitude of sins. I have a few dark spots and this makeup covers well and very smooth. The sponge applicator is what, i believe, make this apply so smoothly. I have used this for years. It feels very light and you don't feel like it's there. I order this on subscription to receive regularly. The price very is reasonable. Definitely will reorder.",
