        {
          "reviewTitle": "Nice Even Coverage & Great Value for The Price",
          "reviewText": "I have had a hard time finding this particular makeup in stores near me. I was happy to find it on Amazon. I have used Cover Girl products since the 70's. I have used more expensive brands over the years and have not been as pleased with them for one reason or another. The CG Aqua Smooth has just the right amount of moisturizer for my skin without being too oily. It is easy to apply and looks natural. The scent is light and pleasant. My skin has changed over the years. I am so glad that I can still use Cover Girl products. Brings back memories of it being my first makeup.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on August 28, 2025",
